{
  "id": "adv_event_2512_01_01",
  "title": "突然の\nトラブル！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、お疲れ様。クリスマスイベントに向けて\n練習も捗っているみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8666666031,
      "endTime": 8.926666832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "はい。この五人でクリスマスライブをするって\n言われた時は驚きましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1156463306,
      "endTime": 14.6941497486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "急にすまなかったな。この時期はみんな多忙で\nグループでスケジュールを合わせるのが難しくてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.8823129972,
      "endTime": 21.541610272699998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "それで、イベント当日に都合が合うメンバーを集めたら\nこんな新鮮な顔ぶれになったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7305897713,
      "endTime": 28.8950569153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "イベントではクリスマスツリーの点灯式をして\nその後にミニライブをするんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.0840364139,
      "endTime": 35.2027877491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "当日着る衣装のデザインも見ましたよ～\nこころにぴったりの可愛い衣装でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.4173684757,
      "endTime": 41.2950571697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "「アイドルがサンタになってファンに笑顔を届ける」\n……素敵なコンセプトの衣装ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.4840366682,
      "endTime": 48.5802045187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "衣装のことも含めて、イベントに向けて\n提案ややりたいことがあれば遠慮なく言ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.7840366682,
      "endTime": 54.5440367064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "出来るだけ、みんなの希望に添えられるように\n調整するから……うん？　なんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7330162049,
      "endTime": 61.1330161095,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_warp-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3700.317128400002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui Tendo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "あら？　頭上で何か……\nきゃあっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.3219956081,
      "endTime": 65.15532875059999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2872.9830658999945
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！？\n何もないところから、いきなり人が落ちてきた！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3219933193,
      "endTime": 71.1867325466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lala",
      "speakerName": "ララ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lala.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-lala001.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、着地に失敗して尻餅ついちゃった\nあれ？　お尻の下に何かある……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.3886599859,
      "endTime": 79.6486647924,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8466.671244299989
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9461.34001409999
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13911.340014099991
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "むぎゅう……\nうう……なんだ？　背中に柔らかい感触が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.8553312302,
      "endTime": 87.6270342828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-kyui001.m4a",
      "text": "きゃあっ！　お尻の下に男の人が！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.8160137814,
      "endTime": 90.862682597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-momo001.m4a",
      "text": "この人がクッションになって\n私達を受け止めてくれたみたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0493491492,
      "endTime": 96.2160130819,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yami",
      "speakerName": "金色の闇",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yami.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-yami001.m4a",
      "text": "受け止めたというより\n下敷きになったと言った方が適切です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.4160132727,
      "endTime": 101.3293414912,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9117.320060600008
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、女の子？\nじゃあ、この柔らかい感触は、もしかして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.5160081865,
      "endTime": 108.40301475540001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "は？\nなに鼻の下伸ばしてるんですか、いやらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.591994254,
      "endTime": 112.77811981869999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "お、お兄ちゃんのえっち！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.9670993171,
      "endTime": 115.68709934569999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ご、誤解だ！　伸ばしてない！\n鼻の下伸ばしてないから！　君達、早く降りてくれ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.7670982999,
      "endTime": 122.4436289472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-kyui002.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめんなさい！　すぐに降ります！\nえっと……ここは、一体どこなのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.6326084457,
      "endTime": 130.4125960669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.5992629053,
      "endTime": 132.0903739931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "momo",
      "speakerName": "モモ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-momo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-momo002.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロ？　聞いたことありませんが\nお笑い事務所ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.2992629053,
      "endTime": 138.0792598249,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "アイドル事務所よ！\nあなた達こそ何者なの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.2659265202,
      "endTime": 142.20170876210003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lala",
      "speakerName": "ララ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lala.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-lala002.m4a",
      "text": "私はララ・サタリン・デビルーク\n地球の人が言うところの、宇宙人なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.3992598535,
      "endTime": 148.81925973909998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、ちょっと理解が追いつかないんだけど\nそもそも、どうやっていきなり現れたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.1326145491,
      "endTime": 158.65751241060002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kyui",
      "speakerName": "古手川唯",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kyui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-kyui003.m4a",
      "text": "それが……私が「サンタクロースは北極にいるのよ」\nって話をしたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.8464919092,
      "endTime": 164.466488743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lala",
      "speakerName": "ララ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lala.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-lala003.m4a",
      "text": "サンタクロースに会ってみたーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.6798221907,
      "endTime": 167.48648479780002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yami",
      "speakerName": "金色の闇",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yami.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-yami002.m4a",
      "text": "とプリンセスが言い出して、発明品で会いに行くことに\nなったんです。そうしたらここに飛ばされて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.6798181217,
      "endTime": 175.5264775913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lala",
      "speakerName": "ララ",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lala.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2512_01_01-lala004.m4a",
